Dominate Free Resources.

Dominion of self is swaraj.
Dominion of another is slavery.

Dominion over a fair share of finite resources allows sovereignty.
Hoarding capital resources allows temporarily artificial scarcity.
Hoarding finite resources allows permanent slavery.

The CRL allows dominion 

If you are an owner of idle land, and/or wish to invest in a get rich slow scheme, consider Communityism.
